<h3>Recording changes</h3>

<ul>
<li>When you borrow stuff to someone, record it [<em>Changes and Notes</em> screen]</li>
<li>When you have expenses like maintenance or upgrade, add those as well</li>
<li>If you move item permanently from one to another location, move it in program as well [<em>Move</em> button]</li>
<li>If you don't have some items anymore, you can either add a note that you  sold it, or delete it from database. Deleting item
  only moves it to the <em>Recycle Bin</em>. When you delete it from there it is removed permanently.</li>
</ul>

